Allowed events: Artie intercepted by the Mayor, Statistical Anomaly alarm active, Artie struggles to hide 1 HP, Mayor wants to exploit build, Artie realizes he is a beacon for power-hungry entities.
Forbidden milestones: none (no new milestones marked DONE in this scene yet).
